1
00:00:05,800 --> 00:00:06,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wrong.</font>

2
00:00:08,820 --> 00:00:10,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Assassinate?</font>

3
00:00:10,700 --> 00:00:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wrong.</font>

4
00:00:13,450 --> 00:00:16,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Play dead?</font>

5
00:00:15,870 --> 00:00:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wrong.</font>

6
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:36,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's "don't fight homicidal maniacs."</font>

7
00:00:39,850 --> 00:00:41,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't understand.</font>

8
00:00:42,220 --> 00:00:47,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've killed people during games.</font>

9
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:55,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that enough for the rest of society 
to consider me a homicidal maniac?</font>

10
00:00:58,050 --> 00:01:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These games are built around survival, 
not killing, as the win condition.</font>

11
00:01:05,300 --> 00:01:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why we've become 
specialized in only that.</font>

12
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:13,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But homicidal maniacs are different.</font>

13
00:01:15,050 --> 00:01:17,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're playing a different game.</font>

14
00:01:18,550 --> 00:01:20,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever you do, don't fight them.</font>

15
00:01:24,570 --> 00:01:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if I'm forced to fight one?</font>

16
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:32,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if it's the only way to win?</font>

17
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:35,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do I do then?</font>

18
00:01:39,450 --> 00:01:41,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Training is over.</font>

19
00:01:43,310 --> 00:01:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Figure the rest out yourself.</font>

20
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:54,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was probably Hakushi's 
so-called "homicidal maniac"</i></font>

21
00:01:54,230 --> 00:01:56,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>who threw the pine cone,</i></font>

22
00:01:57,560 --> 00:02:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but that would mean 
she'd been targeting her.</i></font>

23
00:02:04,790 --> 00:02:08,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Impossible. She'd never 
make a mistake like that.</i></font>

24
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:17,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But there was no other 
plausible explanation.</i></font>

25
00:02:31,790 --> 00:02:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No. That doesn't matter.</i></font>

26
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:46,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What I should be focusing 
on right now is...</i></font>

27
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:53,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>my own survival.</i></font>

28
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:15,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-chan?</font>

29
00:03:25,170 --> 00:03:29,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will happen to me 
if I don't become a swan?</font>

30
00:03:29,810 --> 00:03:30,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

31
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:37,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A duck...</font>

32
00:03:40,780 --> 00:03:46,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I'm still a duck when I grow up...</font>

33
00:03:50,220 --> 00:03:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what should I do?</font>

34
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think you should do?</font>

35
00:04:05,410 --> 00:04:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Me?</font>

36
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:13,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I'm still a duck?</font>

37
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:30,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I like ducks more than swans.</font>

38
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

39
00:04:36,420 --> 00:04:40,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you'll be fine 
even if you stay a duck.</font>

40
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:54,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if I don't become a swan...</font>

41
00:04:58,910 --> 00:05:03,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if I can't do anything about it...</font>

42
00:05:07,630 --> 00:05:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still... That's exactly why...</font>

43
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All I can do is fight back.</font>

44
00:05:44,990 --> 00:05:49,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It will soon be 5 PM on day one.</i></font>

45
00:05:50,030 --> 00:05:52,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It is time for everyone to go home.</i></font>

46
00:06:02,890 --> 00:06:07,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It will soon be 5 PM on day one.</i></font>

47
00:06:07,940 --> 00:06:10,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It is time for everyone to go home.</i></font>

48
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how far it went, 
the sun never got closer.</font>

49
00:06:33,030 --> 00:06:36,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instead, as it gradually grew 
smaller and farther,</font>

50
00:06:37,630 --> 00:06:39,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the sun said...</font>

51
00:06:42,450 --> 00:06:44,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"You are a grey nightjar.</font>

52
00:06:45,380 --> 00:06:48,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. That must be 
quite difficult for you.</font>

53
00:06:50,860 --> 00:06:55,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fly tonight, 
and ask the stars for a favor.</font>

54
00:06:57,530 --> 00:07:01,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, you are not a daytime bird."</font>

55
00:07:08,310 --> 00:07:09,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Moegi-san.</font>

56
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It will soon be 5 PM on day one.</i></font>

57
00:07:13,780 --> 00:07:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good. You're still alive.</font>

58
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:19,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It is time for everyone to go home.</i></font>

59
00:07:17,470 --> 00:07:20,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a serial killer among the rabbits,</font>

60
00:07:20,420 --> 00:07:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so no one can focus on the game.</font>

61
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not leaving, are you?</font>

62
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

63
00:07:28,570 --> 00:07:32,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I felt hopeless by myself. 
I'm glad I ran into you.</font>

64
00:07:33,580 --> 00:07:37,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The situation has become difficult, 
but let's survive together.</font>

65
00:07:38,330 --> 00:07:39,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

66
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, I know it's a lot to ask, 
but may I make a request?</font>

67
00:07:46,940 --> 00:07:49,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have any weapons right now.</font>

68
00:07:50,390 --> 00:07:54,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can afford to 
spare anything, then...</font>

69
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

70
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

71
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One shot will do, right?</font>

72
00:08:10,230 --> 00:08:12,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It is now 5 PM.</i></font>

73
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:16,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The gates will open again 
at 6 AM tomorrow.</i></font>

74
00:08:22,580 --> 00:08:24,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It is now 5 PM.</i></font>

75
00:08:25,170 --> 00:08:29,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The gates will open again 
at 6 AM tomorrow.</i></font>

76
00:08:42,220 --> 00:08:44,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I ran into a rabbit.</i></font>

77
00:08:51,130 --> 00:08:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She was like a ghost.</i></font>

78
00:11:02,070 --> 00:11:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

79
00:12:00,370 --> 00:12:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Their experience levels 
were too different.</i></font>

80
00:12:04,740 --> 00:12:09,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No matter what I tried to do, 
the ghost was always one step ahead.</i></font>

81
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:12,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At this rate...</i></font>

82
00:12:18,570 --> 00:12:20,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I thought if I killed my parents...</i></font>

83
00:12:27,750 --> 00:12:31,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I could just kill my parents,</i></font>

84
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>then I could be like Kyara-san.</i></font>

85
00:12:44,780 --> 00:12:51,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew that a grey nightjar 
could never become a whale.</i></font>

86
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:53,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's not...</i></font>

87
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:57,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's just not...</i></font>

88
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:06,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love you.</font>

89
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:13,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Apparently, that was how Moegi 
interpreted her exhalation.</i></font>

90
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love you.</font>

91
00:13:19,300 --> 00:13:24,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Because it was something 
she'd never received before,</i></font>

92
00:13:26,030 --> 00:13:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>she didn't understand 
exactly what it was, but...</i></font>

93
00:13:35,150 --> 00:13:36,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love you.</font>

94
00:13:38,540 --> 00:13:41,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That warmth</i></font>

95
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>was her final remaining reason to live.</i></font>

96
00:13:50,990 --> 00:13:56,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if a grey nightjar 
can't reach that star,</font>

97
00:13:59,030 --> 00:14:00,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

98
00:14:02,810 --> 00:14:05,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will keep fighting.</font>

99
00:14:09,190 --> 00:14:12,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I refuse to lose here.</font>

100
00:14:14,820 --> 00:14:18,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I am Kyara-san's student!</font>

101
00:14:37,330 --> 00:14:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My nerves burned with pain.</i></font>

102
00:14:43,570 --> 00:14:49,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think I took another blow 
to my shoulder and stomach,</i></font>

103
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:54,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I couldn't tell where anymore.</i></font>

104
00:14:58,090 --> 00:15:05,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't even understand why 
the ghost woman made that face,</i></font>

105
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:13,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but apparently, it was over.</i></font>

106
00:15:16,690 --> 00:15:22,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It meant I didn't have to 
pretend to be strong anymore.</i></font>

107
00:15:25,260 --> 00:15:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I haven't felt this way 
since I killed my parents.</i></font>

108
00:15:33,490 --> 00:15:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, what?</i></font>

109
00:15:35,510 --> 00:15:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How did the grey nightjar end up?</i></font>

110
00:15:42,670 --> 00:15:45,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It couldn't become a star, and then...</i></font>

111
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:55,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Whatever. I'll have Kyara-san 
read it to me again.</i></font>

112
00:15:58,130 --> 00:16:05,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In any case, until my very 
last breath, I, Moegi...</i></font>

113
00:16:09,500 --> 00:16:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>until my very last breath...</i></font>

114
00:16:22,620 --> 00:16:25,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>cried tears of frustration.</i></font>

115
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And so, the grey nightjar's 
star continued to burn.</font>

116
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It kept burning and burning and burning.</font>

117
00:17:38,590 --> 00:17:43,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's still burning to this day.</font>

118
00:17:56,540 --> 00:17:59,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was inconsequential.</i></font>

119
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She lacked talent. 
That was the only way to put it.</i></font>

120
00:18:07,790 --> 00:18:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Apparently, she was the 
homicidal maniac's student,</i></font>

121
00:18:11,770 --> 00:18:14,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but she surely lacked potential.</i></font>

122
00:18:15,710 --> 00:18:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if we'd repeated the 
same events a hundred times,</i></font>

123
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:25,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that stump would've lost every time.</i></font>

124
00:18:28,530 --> 00:18:34,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But still, she saw it.</i></font>

125
00:18:35,510 --> 00:18:38,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her face as she died.</i></font>

126
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:47,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She poured all of her being into 
reaching for it and still failed.</i></font>

127
00:18:48,190 --> 00:18:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How could she compensate a loser 
who'd lived the best she could</i></font>

128
00:18:57,150 --> 00:18:59,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but whose efforts didn't pay off?</i></font>

129
00:19:00,180 --> 00:19:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yuki couldn't begin 
to guess what that was,</i></font>

130
00:19:06,150 --> 00:19:09,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and she couldn't begin 
to sympathize if asked,</i></font>

131
00:19:10,100 --> 00:19:14,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but there was still something there.</i></font>

132
00:19:15,210 --> 00:19:19,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was different from Yuki's 
feelings of "just because."</i></font>

133
00:19:20,280 --> 00:19:26,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>By continuing to play these games 
and live in this world,</i></font>

134
00:19:26,490 --> 00:19:31,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>there was something she could achieve.</i></font>

135
00:19:37,050 --> 00:19:42,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And Yuki killed that.</i></font>

136
00:19:47,330 --> 00:19:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone living "just because"...</i></font>

137
00:19:55,870 --> 00:20:04,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, a practical ghost who 
wasn't even really alive...</i></font>

138
00:20:06,740 --> 00:20:13,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>depending on her innate talent.</i></font>

139
00:20:23,220 --> 00:20:29,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hakushi had taught her how 
to emotionally prepare herself.</i></font>

140
00:20:30,630 --> 00:20:36,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Take a couple of slow breaths.</i></font>

141
00:20:39,330 --> 00:20:47,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But not even that technique 
could clear her mind.</i></font>

142
00:20:48,890 --> 00:20:53,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No matter how many times she breathed,</i></font>

143
00:20:54,660 --> 00:20:57,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>nothing changed.</i></font>

144
00:20:59,360 --> 00:21:05,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Eventually, even the beating 
of her own heart</i></font>

145
00:21:05,610 --> 00:21:09,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>felt strange to Yuki.</i></font>

146
00:21:10,210 --> 00:21:17,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A part of her couldn't accept 
that the stump had died</i></font>

147
00:21:17,630 --> 00:21:20,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>while she still lived.</i></font>

148
00:21:22,320 --> 00:21:28,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If she encountered the homicidal 
maniac in that state, she'd die.</i></font>

149
00:21:32,970 --> 00:21:40,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still, her legs didn't stop walking.</i></font>

150
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How do I have legs</i></font>

151
00:21:50,910 --> 00:21:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>when I'm not a ghost?</i></font>

152
00:22:12,490 --> 00:22:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that incredible?</font>

153
00:22:26,580 --> 00:22:28,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome home.</font>

